@startuml
title 미핏 - 분석 리포트 생성 파이프라인 시퀀스 (interview-analysis-report 5+ 단계 zoom-in)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ActorBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantBorderColor #2196F3
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantFontSize 11
  BoxBorderColor #B0BEC5
  BoxBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
}

actor "사용자" as U
participant "Backend\n(Django)" as BE
queue "Redis\nanalysis 큐" as Q
participant "interview-analysis-report\nWorker" as W
participant "ReportGenerator\nService" as RG
participant "VoiceAnalysis\nInvoker" as VAI
participant "LLMAnalyzer" as LLMA
participant "VideoAnalysis\nAggregator" as VAA
participant "voice-analyzer\nLambda" as Lambda
participant "OpenAI\n(gpt-4o-mini)" as LLM
database "PostgreSQL\n(SQLAlchemy)" as DB
participant "S3\n(resume bundle)" as S3

== Step 0. 트리거 (Backend → analysis 큐) ==

U -> BE : POST /api/v1/interviews/{uuid}/generate-report/
activate BE
  BE -> BE : 티켓 차감 (UseTicketsService)
  BE -> DB : AnalysisReport(status=PENDING) 생성
  BE -> Q : dispatch\nanalysis.tasks.generate_report.generate_analysis_report\n(report_id, bundle_url)
  BE --> U : 202 Accepted
deactivate BE

Q -> W : pull task
activate W
  W -> RG : ReportGeneratorService().generate(report_id, bundle_url)
  activate RG

== Step 1. Load (순차) ==

  RG -> DB : SELECT AnalysisReportTable WHERE id = report_id
  RG -> DB : SELECT InterviewSessionTable
  RG -> DB : SELECT InterviewTurnTable\nORDER BY turn_number, followup_order
  RG -> S3 : GET resume bundle.json\n(bundle_url)
  S3 --> RG : { sections, embeddings_meta, ... }
  RG -> DB : SELECT JobDescriptionTable\n(via UserJobDescription)

== Step 2. InterviewBehaviorAnalysis 보장 ==

  loop turn in turns
    RG -> DB : INSERT InterviewBehaviorAnalysisTable\n(turn_id, status="pending")
  end

== Step 3. 음성 분석 (병렬 Lambda 호출) ==

  RG -> VAI : analyze_all_turns(session_id)
  activate VAI
  par ThreadPoolExecutor (max_workers=4)
    VAI -> Lambda : invoke pj-kmucd1-04-mefit-voice-analyzer\n{ scaled_audio_key }
    activate Lambda
      Lambda --> VAI : { speechDurationMs, totalDurationMs,\n  silenceRatio, silenceSegmentCount,\n  avgDbfsSpeech, timeline[...] }
    deactivate Lambda
  else 다른 turn (병렬)
    VAI -> Lambda : invoke voice-analyzer\n(다른 audio_key)
    Lambda --> VAI : voice metrics
  end
  VAI --> RG : { turn_id: voice_data, ... }
  deactivate VAI

  note right of RG
    실패 시: voice 데이터 없이
    LLM 분석은 계속 진행 (graceful degrade)
  end note

== Step 4. LLM 분석 (gpt-4o-mini, 4 텍스트 카테고리) ==

  RG -> LLMA : analyze(context)\n{ session, turns, resume, JD, voice_summary }
  activate LLMA
  LLMA -> LLM : ChatOpenAI.invoke(\n  prompt,\n  callback=TokenUsageCallback,\n  temperature=0.3\n)
  activate LLM
    note right of LLM
      4 텍스트 카테고리 평가:
      ① 구체성 (STAR 기법, 정량 지표)
      ② 직무 적합성 (JD duties / requirements 매칭)
      ③ 논리성 (전후 일관성)
      ④ 신뢰도 (이력서 정합성)
    end note
    LLM --> LLMA : AnalysisResult\n(category_scores, question_feedbacks,\n strengths, improvement_areas)
  deactivate LLM
  LLMA -> LLMA : TokenUsageCallback\n→ input/output_tokens, cost_usd
  LLMA --> RG : AnalysisResult
  deactivate LLMA

== Step 5. 영상 분석 집계 (사전 계산된 결과 읽기) ==

  RG -> VAA : aggregate(session_id)
  activate VAA
    VAA -> DB : SELECT InterviewRecordingTable\n  .face_analysis_result\n  (face-analyzer Lambda 가 미리 저장)
    VAA -> DB : SELECT InterviewTurnTable\n  .gaze_away_count
    VAA -> VAA : gaze_score = (1 - avg_gaze_dev) × 100\nface_score = (avg_neutral + avg_positive) × 100\nvideo_score = round(gaze × 0.6 + face × 0.4)
    VAA --> RG : VideoAnalysisResult\n(video_score, video_analysis_comment, per_turn)
  deactivate VAA

  note right of VAA
    face-analyzer Lambda 는
    S3 영상 업로드 시점에 별도 호출됨
    (sequence-interview-full-flow Step 4 참조)
  end note

== Step 6. 음성 점수 집계 (rule-based) ==

  RG -> RG : _aggregate_audio_analysis()\n속도 / 필러 / 침묵 / 음량 페널티 계산
  RG -> RG : audio_score = 100 - 페널티\naudio_analysis_comment 생성

== Step 7. 종합 점수 ==

  RG -> RG : overall_score = round(\n  content × 0.50 + audio × 0.25 + video × 0.25\n)\noverall_grade = score_to_grade(overall)

== Step 8. DB 저장 (단일 트랜잭션) ==

  RG -> DB : UPDATE AnalysisReportTable\n  SET overall_score, overall_grade,\n      content_score, audio_score, video_score,\n      category_scores (JSONB),\n      question_feedbacks (JSONB),\n      strengths, improvement_areas,\n      audio_analysis_result, video_analysis_result,\n      status="completed", updated_at=now()
  RG -> DB : INSERT TokenUsageTable\n  (token_usable=AnalysisReport,\n   model_name, input/output/total_tokens, cost_usd)
  loop turn in turns
    RG -> DB : UPDATE InterviewBehaviorAnalysisTable\n  SET speech_data (JSONB), status="completed"
  end
  deactivate RG
deactivate W

== Step 9. SSE 알림 (별도 다이어그램 참조) ==

note over BE, U
  분석 완료 알림은
  sequence-realtime-notification.puml 의
  "면접 분석 리포트 완료" 이벤트로 처리
end note

footer MeFit - 분석 리포트 5+단계 (FR-REPORT-01~07) — content + audio + video 가중 평균
@enduml
